Package: FERRET
Type: Package
Title: Unified methods for the inference and analysis of gene regulatory networks
Version: 1.5.4
Date: 2023-09-25
Authors@R: person("Tara", "Eicher",
                        email = "teicher@hsph.harvard.edu",role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1809-4458"))
Maintainer: Tara Eicher <teicher@hsph.harvard.edu>
Description: FERRET is a framework to evaluate robustness of gene regulatory network inference methods using single-cell data sets. It implements the RAUC and monotonicity metrics as well as facilitating pathway analysis.
